nodes.text: The Black Ivory Quintuplets were a group of criminals active during the Imperial Era. The group's members were killed by the bounty hunter IG-88, who chose not to immediately claim the bounty on them. After capturing IG-88 and discovering the bounties stored in his head, a group of criminals led by Kaluub Akjee attempted to claim the bounty on the Black Ivory Quintuplets, among several others.
